# tssplit - Trivial split for strings with escaped characters and quotes

## Installation
```shell script
pip install tssplit
```

## Usage
```python
from tssplit import tssplit

tssplit('ooooo/ooo|/ooo"XXX/XXX"ooo/"ooo/ooooo',  quote='"', delimiter='/', escape='|')
['ooooo', 'ooo/oooXXX/XXXooo', 'ooo/ooooo']
```

